Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> start
Rule 1     start -> bloc
Rule 2     bloc -> bloc statement SEMI
Rule 3     bloc -> statement SEMI
Rule 4     statement -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LACC bloc RACC
Rule 5     statement -> IF LPAREN expression RPAREN LACC bloc RACC ELSE LACC bloc RACC
Rule 6     statement -> WHILE LPAREN expression RPAREN LACC bloc RACC
Rule 7     statement -> FOR LPAREN statement SEMI expression SEMI statement RPAREN LACC bloc RACC
Rule 8     statement -> NAME PLUSEGAL expression
Rule 9     statement -> NAME PLUSPLUS
Rule 10    statement -> PRINT LPAREN expression RPAREN
Rule 11    statement -> NAME EGAL expression
Rule 12    expression -> expression INF expression
Rule 13    expression -> expression INFEG expression
Rule 14    expression -> expression SUP expression
Rule 15    expression -> expression EGALEGAL expression
Rule 16    expression -> expression AND expression
Rule 17    expression -> expression OR expression
Rule 18    expression -> expression PLUS expression
Rule 19    expression -> expression TIMES expression
Rule 20    expression -> expression MINUS expression
Rule 21    expression -> expression DIVIDE expression
Rule 22    expression -> LPAREN expression RPAREN
Rule 23    expression -> NUMBER
Rule 24    expression -> NAME

Terminals, with rules where they appear

AND                  : 16
DIVIDE               : 21
EGAL                 : 11
EGALEGAL             : 15
ELSE                 : 5
FOR                  : 7
IF                   : 4 5
INF                  : 12
INFEG                : 13
LACC                 : 4 5 5 6 7
LPAREN               : 4 5 6 7 10 22
MINUS                : 20
NAME                 : 8 9 11 24
NUMBER               : 23
OR                   : 17
PLUS                 : 18
PLUSEGAL             : 8
PLUSPLUS             : 9
PRINT                : 10
RACC                 : 4 5 5 6 7
RPAREN               : 4 5 6 7 10 22
SEMI                 : 2 3 7 7
SUP                  : 14
TIMES                : 19
WHILE                : 6
error                : 

Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

bloc                 : 1 2 4 5 5 6 7
expression           : 4 5 6 7 8 10 11 12 12 13 13 14 14 15 15 16 16 17 17 18 18 19 19 20 20 21 21 22
start                : 0
statement            : 2 3 7 7

